{"tid":682352,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"皇馬成全熱刺！熱刺歐聯順利升檔 利物浦淒慘...","createTime":"2018-05-28T21:21:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-29T06:40:24.000Z","uid":147522,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6664e38fc281995db0ce07318ace6cc636fbfe2b","tid":682352,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T21:21:25.000Z","msg":"　　《每日郵報》報導，利物浦歐聯決賽輸波間接幫助了熱刺，熱刺因此成為歐聯第二檔球隊。<br />\n　　今季熱刺是歐聯第三檔球隊，小組賽和皇馬、多蒙特等強敵分在一組。 　　<br />\n　　不過皇馬奪冠後升入第一檔，空出了他們此前在第二檔的位置，熱刺是第三檔排名最高的球隊，他們因此升上第二檔。<br />\n<br />\n　　利物浦是下季歐聯中排名最低的英超球隊，他們歐聯決賽失利後錯失升入第一檔的機會，只能暫時落入第三檔。<br />\n　　不過如果第二檔的賓菲加和巴素利歐聯資格賽都遭淘汰，利物浦就可以進入第二檔。"},{"pid":"8d7eebbf6075223fbcfd02f804590b859ed43841","tid":682352,"uid":30468,"like":30,"dislike":2,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T21:23:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/29/052308_909a2997844a88c656d40b9dbfa55cc3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F29%2F052308_909a2997844a88c656d40b9dbfa55cc3.gif&h=4f3cd3e1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d6727ee4ff780caa345bafd027b5f425eac7c884","tid":682352,"uid":106165,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8d7eebbf6075223fbcfd02f804590b859ed43841","tid":682352,"uid":30468,"like":30,"dislike":2,"score":28,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T21:23:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/29/052308_909a2997844a88c656d40b9dbfa55cc3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F29%2F052308_909a2997844a88c656d40b9dbfa55cc3.gif&h=4f3cd3e1&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T23:17:33.000Z","msg":"屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeff4043e0bed63843c5ce3b9e5ce4aaaddd6be9","tid":682352,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T23:21:53.000Z","msg":"乜撚野第一檔第二檔。。。"},{"pid":"80ea8d0c2ae4996d1b7199df3d